Dear Patient,

Welcome to MediCare! We are delighted to have you as part of our healthcare family.

Your patient profile has been successfully created. Here is everything you need to know to get started:

YOUR NEXT STEPS:

  1. Complete Your Health Profile
     Help us serve you better by filling in your medical history and current medications.
     https://patient.medicareclinic.com/profile

  2. Book Your First Appointment
     Schedule a consultation with one of our specialists at your convenience.
     https://patient.medicareclinic.com/appointments

  3. Download the MediCare App
     Access your health records, prescriptions, and lab reports anytime.
     https://patient.medicareclinic.com/app

  4. Set Up Emergency Contact
     Ensure we can reach your loved ones when needed.
     https://patient.medicareclinic.com/emergency-contact

IMPORTANT CONTACT INFORMATION:
  - 24/7 Helpline: 1800-MED-CARE (1800-633-2273)
  - Appointments: appointments@medicareclinic.com
  - General Enquiries: info@medicareclinic.com

Your health and well-being are our top priority. We look forward to being your trusted healthcare partner.

Warm regards,
Patient Care Team
MediCare Clinic
www.medicareclinic.com

